import random
import sys

sys.stdin = open('inputs/pairs_in.txt')

def main():

    print(a)


if __name__ == '__main__':

#Get the number of integers
n = int(input())

#Get the integers
a = [int(x) for x in input().split()]

#Sort the integers
a = sorted(a)

#Get the maximum value
max_val = max(a)

#Get the sum of the integers
sum_val = sum(a)

#Get the sum of the integers with the maximum integer
sum_val_max = sum_val - max_val

#Get the difference between the sum of the integers and the sum of the integers with the maximum integer
diff = sum_val - sum_val_max

#Print the difference
print(diff)
